# Fast Client

Simple API Client. Fast and easy to use.

# Features

- [x] GET/POST/PUT/DELETE/PATCH
- [x] Async support
- [x] File Upload
- [x] Streaming Response
- [x] Retry
- [x] Timeout
- [x] Pydantic Response validation
- [x] Auth using headers
- [ ] Rate Limit
- [ ] Advanced auth

